This terraform code will create one ansible server and server to deploy K8S
This will deploy ansible on the ansible k8s_servers
Investigating to see if kubernetes using kubespray can also be installed

Running instructions:
Create a ssh key and upload the public key to your digitalocean account
Terraform init from the directory
Terraform plan -var "pvt_key=path to key"
Changing the resources only for the required resources to keep the cost low, uncomment required providers when needed
